OOC: Hot Rod is in his room in the Alliance base. He had been talking to
Feline, and do to reprograming she didn't know who he was. He put a note
under her door that said: I love you. I'm going back to the Maximals.
I'll be back for you. Blah Blah Blah. He also put one of his medals with
the note for her to have for the hell of it.(Think Navy 'wings' but with
an Autobot symbol in the center. He couldn't get out of the base do to
the lockdown, so he is waiting in his room, to get out.
